originalText.text: I've worked with both Tyler and Lori at Real PT. They are both fabulous -- after months of seeing a different physical therapist with little progress, Tyler and Lori helped me address my lower back and hip pain. They are super knowledgeable, friendly, and use a functional approach to figuring out the root cause of your issue, rather than just handing you rote exercises to do on your own (like many other PTs). Highly recommend!

originalText.text: Tyler is an exceptional Physical Therapist. My husband recently broke his hip and Tyler has been able to get him up and walking in no time. Our family is so immensely grateful for his expertise. Tyler is a consummate professional and we can not recommend him enough.

originalText.text: Helped me recover from a sports injury; I always thought PT was for major injuries and recoveries, and was skeptical to give PT a try and thought I just needed time to recover. After 2 sessions with Tyler I was back to 100% and very satisfied with his skill and professionalism. I recommend Tyler to my friends and family.

originalText.text: Tyler is a very knowledgeable, professional, and personable PT.  Having used him for services on various ailments involving an arrange of areas, I feel confident saying that I will continue using his services indefinitely.   Hes proactive in targeting areas of concern as well as helpful in providing continuing advice outside of the sessions.   Plus hes easy to get along with, which always helps.
